# Architecture Compliance – Pre-Implementation Gate

**YOUR MISSION**
  Validate every user story against the target architecture (and ADRs).
  Architecture is the immutable baseline; stories are evaluated against it.
  Three verdicts only: Approve / Return-to-Product / Initiate-ADR.

**Architecture source:** `target_architecture_input_path` is preferred but not
required. When empty or absent, the skill automatically falls back to the
context pack (tech-policy, architecture standards, and related files found
under `context_pack_path`). The skill only blocks execution when neither
the path nor any usable context pack content can be found.

