| target_architecture_path | string | Preferred | Path to target architecture folder — omit to use context pack fallback | ./artifacts/outputs/software-architecture/target-architecture |
| context_pack_path | string | No | Context pack folder for architecture fallback | ./context-pack |
| adr_path | string | No | Path to ADR catalog | ./artifacts/outputs/software-architecture/adrs |
