compliance_path: directory, compliance_status: Aggregated verdict: PASSED (all stories APPROVE) | PARTIAL (some RETURN_TO_PRODUCT but no ADR-required) | FAILED (any INITIATE_ADR), approve_count: integer, return_to_product_count: integer, initiate_adr_count: integer, compliance_feedback: One-line-per-non-approved-story summary. Format: [VERDICT] [STORY_ID] [GAP CATEGORIES] per line. Empty when all stories APPROVE.

