48: - **Loops:** Traditional and modern iteration patterns\n49: - **DOM Manipulation:** Event handling, element modification\n50: ", "metadata": {"start_line": 1, "end_line": 50, "returned_lines": 50, "has_more": true, "eof_reached": false, "truncated": false}}}
